race.comment: ENGLISH CONQUEROR (2) two career runs have been full of merit, including latest fourth over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Will sit on the speed and prove hard to get past. JUST RESPONSE (4) tipped straight out after his fading debut third over 1200m at Newcastle last June. Has impressed in two trials wins and he looks set for a positive return. LOGAN DOWNS (5) showed good early speed on debut as fav before folding up late when a plugging fourth over 1300m at Newcastle. Expecting a better performance at this level with race experience on his side. REGAL PROBLEM (7) resumes after the two respectable runs in her first campaign. Up in trip and grade when a tiring sixth over 1250m at Canterbury. Two good trials can see her take a hand in the finish from the inside gate.
